job.title: Mazagon Dock Non-Executive Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 1388 Non-Executive Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Non-Executive 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for 12th pass has been published by Mazagon Dock Shipbuilders Ltd for Non-Executive vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Non-Executive, from 11-06-2021, and till 04-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

The mode of application is Online

  • The application fee for GEN/ OBC/ EWS Category category candidates is only Rs. 100/-
  • The application fee for SC/ ST/ PWD Category category candidates is Nil

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Non-Executive in Mazagon Dock, your SSC/ HSC, Diploma/ Degree (Engg.) must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 11-06-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 04-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 37 years old. 

Mazagon Dock Non-Executive Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed vacancies:

How to apply for Mazagon Dock Non-Executive Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Non-Executive. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of Mazagon Dock and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Mazagon Dock
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
